    Megatron had to decide.....ally with the Allience, one of the most 
influencial and power factions, or remain with the Predacons and help them 
become the ultimate power on this planet. He looked up to the sky, as if it 
held the answer....
    "Kitkat, I belive I have just made a descicion that will change my life, 
how ever long it may be....." He trailed off, without saying his little catch 
phrase. "So be it, the Predacons will rule this planet. The Allience shall 
fall before us, just as the Maximals will be crushed under the heel of our 
boot. The Iron fist of Predacon rule has been long missed. It is time for us 
to take hold of this planet...once and for all. Yes....." 
    Megatron now smiled. As did Aracnia. Three forces, together at last, that 
will see the downfall of two empires, and several pathetic factions that 
should have been weeded out long ago.
    "Now that things are settled, when shall we take on the Allience? my 
troops can be ready and mobil in less than an hour. "Aracnia said, letting 
her claw slide across her womb, filled with another bos spark.
